author: Seally7712
title: Decent
review:
This set is very good overall, there are only two main flaws, one being the connection of two vent like pieces to the lower torso, the vent piece is a one by two. While the connection point is a one by one tile. That is flaw one, flaw two is that war machine doesn't fit inside the mech unless you take off his gun.

Overall i give this set a B+.(LegoLad Reviews)

author: Nat501
title: Very good buy but inaccurate to the movie
review:
This is a very playable set with some interesting piece usage and great Minifigures even if Rhodey doesn't have his arc reactor

The set doesn't appear in Endgame though like all the other sets in the wave
